{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "claude-code", "elements": [{"type": "text", "id": "title", "x": 60, "y": 10, "width": 800, "height": 24, "text": "Стек ФАПИ.СЕК: процедурный слой FAPI с отечественной криптографией", "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "wrap", "x": 280, "y": 50, "width": 380, "height": 320, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid"}, {"type": "text", "id": "wrap-label", "x": 290, "y": 58, "width": 360, "height": 18, "text": "СТО БР ФАПИ.СЕК-1.6-2024  (приказ № ОД-1615 от 07.10.2024)", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "base", "x": 300, "y": 320, "width": 340, "height": 40, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "#f1f3f5", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#868e96", "strokeWidth": 2, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "txt-base"}]}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt-base", "x": 352.0, "y": 331.2, "width": 236.0, "height": 17.6, "containerId": "base", "text": "OAuth 2.0  +  OpenID Connect Core", "fontSize": 13.0, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "lineHeight": 1.35}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "fapi", "x": 300, "y": 240, "width": 340, "height": 70, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "#e5dbff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#8b5cf6", "strokeWidth": 2, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "txt-fapi"}]}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt-fapi", "x": 376.2, "y": 252.7, "width": 187.6, "height": 44.6, "containerId": "fapi", "text": "FAPI 1.0 Advanced  +  JARM\nбазовый и расширенный профили,\nrequest object, mTLS, PKCE S256", "fontSize": 11.0, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "lineHeight": 1.35}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "crypto", "x": 300, "y": 160, "width": 165, "height": 70, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#f59e0b", "strokeWidth": 2, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "txt-crypto"}]}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt-crypto", "x": 319.2, "y": 174.8, "width": 126.5, "height": 40.5, "containerId": "crypto", "text": "Криптография в JOSE\n(JWS / JWE / JWT / JWK)\nи в подписи запросов", "fontSize": 10.0, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "lineHeight": 1.35}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "tls", "x": 475, "y": 160, "width": 165, "height": 70, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#f59e0b", "strokeWidth": 2, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "txt-tls"}]}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt-tls", "x": 499.8, "y": 174.8, "width": 115.5, "height": 40.5, "containerId": "tls", "text": "Транспортный слой:\nвзаимный TLS\nна сертификатах X.509", "fontSize": 10.0, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "lineHeight": 1.35}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "intl-crypto", "x": 30, "y": 130, "width": 230, "height": 60, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "strokeStyle": "dashed", "strokeWidth": 2, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "txt-intl-crypto"}]}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt-intl-crypto", "x": 70.8, "y": 139.8, "width": 148.5, "height": 40.5, "containerId": "intl-crypto", "text": "Международная криптография:\nRSA / ECDSA, SHA-2, AES\n— не применяется в JOSE", "fontSize": 10.0, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "lineHeight": 1.35}, {"type": "arrow", "id": "ar-intl-crypto", "x": 260, "y": 175, "width": 40, "height": 20, "points": [[0, 0], [40, 20]], "endArrowhead": "arrow", "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "strokeStyle": "dashed", "strokeWidth": 1.5}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "intl-tls", "x": 30, "y": 220, "width": 230, "height": 60, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "strokeStyle": "dashed", "strokeWidth": 2, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "txt-intl-tls"}]}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt-intl-tls", "x": 65.2, "y": 229.8, "width": 159.5, "height": 40.5, "containerId": "intl-tls", "text": "TLS 1.2/1.3 с международными\nкриптонаборами\n— не применяется в транспорте", "fontSize": 10.0, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "lineHeight": 1.35}, {"type": "arrow", "id": "ar-intl-tls", "x": 260, "y": 250, "width": 215, "height": -20, "points": [[0, 0], [215, 0], [215, -20]], "endArrowhead": "arrow", "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "strokeStyle": "dashed", "strokeWidth": 1.5}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "gost-crypto", "x": 680, "y": 130, "width": 230, "height": 60, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "#c3fae8", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#06b6d4", "strokeWidth": 2, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "txt-gost-crypto"}]}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt-gost-crypto", "x": 704.2, "y": 139.8, "width": 181.5, "height": 40.5, "containerId": "gost-crypto", "text": "ГОСТ-криптография в JOSE:\n34.10 (подпись), 34.11 «Стрибог»,\n34.12 «Кузнечик» / «Магма»", "fontSize": 10.0, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "lineHeight": 1.35}, {"type": "arrow", "id": "ar-gost-crypto", "x": 680, "y": 175, "points": [[0, 0], [-215, 20]], "endArrowhead": "arrow", "strokeColor": "#06b6d4", "strokeWidth": 2}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "gost-tls", "x": 680, "y": 220, "width": 230, "height": 60, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "#c3fae8", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#06b6d4", "strokeWidth": 2, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "txt-gost-tls"}]}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt-gost-tls", "x": 712.5, "y": 229.8, "width": 165.0, "height": 40.5, "containerId": "gost-tls", "text": "ГОСТ TLS в транспорте,\nсертификаты УЦ Банка России,\nключи в сертифицированном СКЗИ", "fontSize": 10.0, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "lineHeight": 1.35}, {"type": "arrow", "id": "ar-gost-tls", "x": 680, "y": 235, "points": [[0, 0], [-40, -45]], "endArrowhead": "arrow", "strokeColor": "#06b6d4", "strokeWidth": 2}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "tk26", "x": 680, "y": 50, "width": 230, "height": 60, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#f59e0b", "strokeWidth": 1.5, "strokeStyle": "dashed", "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "txt-tk26"}]}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt-tk26", "x": 723.5, "y": 59.8, "width": 143.0, "height": 40.5, "containerId": "tk26", "text": "ТК 26 МР 26.2.002-2024:\nприменение алгоритмов ГОСТ\nв JWS / JWE / JWT / JWK", "fontSize": 10.0, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "lineHeight": 1.35}, {"type": "arrow", "id": "ar-tk26", "x": 795, "y": 110, "points": [[0, 0], [0, 18]], "endArrowhead": "arrow", "strokeColor": "#f59e0b", "strokeStyle": "dashed", "strokeWidth": 1.5}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "note", "x": 30, "y": 395, "width": 880, "height": 50, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "strokeStyle": "dashed", "strokeWidth": 1, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "txt-note"}]}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt-note", "x": 82.2, "y": 413.2, "width": 775.5, "height": 13.5, "containerId": "note", "text": "Процедурный стек в центре наследуется от OIDF FAPI без изменений; криптография и транспорт обеспечиваются отечественными провайдерами справа.", "fontSize": 10.0, "fontFamily": 5, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "lineHeight": 1.35}], "appState": {"viewBackgroundColor": "#ffffff", "gridSize": null}, "files": {}}